                  Coiffeur</a>
              </li>
              <li class="menu-search-item">
                <a href="{{ path('home',{activity: "epicerie"})}}" class="menu-search-link"><img
                    src="https://img.icons8.com/windows/32/000000/shopping-basket.png" width="25px" alt="shop-icon" />&ensp;
